casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Wozniak, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Wozniak (2001), 93 Ohio St.3d 173.]

(Nos. 00-2014 and 00-2157 Submitted January 9, 2001 Decided September 19, 2001.) Ron O’Brien, Franklin County Prosecuting Attorney, and Sarah W. Thompson, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee. David L. Strait, Franklin County Public Defender, for appellant.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed on the authority of State v. Thompson (2001), 92 Ohio St.3d 584, 752 N.E.2d 276.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
